<span id="freeTextContainer16527425378139686396">Dave Lewis is a Welsh writer based in Pontypridd, south Wales.<br/><br/>Dave has been widely published all over the world in a number of literary magazines and web sites. He has published a number of books and his work has included poetry, prose, short stories, photography, haiku, travel, comedy and crime novels.<br/><br/><a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://www.david-lewis.co.uk'>www.david-lewis.co.uk</a><br/><br/></span>
